<br>
Mobs still not summon (well not most of them) so you still see Shamans, Necros and druids root-dott.<br>
<br>
You still see druids and wizards Quading in ... Well everywhere, you even see them quading Golems in PoV (and gaining like 35% AA a quad).<br>
<br>
You see SKs solo those Golems in PoV.<br>
<br>
If they want to get soloing to stop they should make ALL L45+ mobs summon, they need to make it snare have a random chance of break, they need to make it so DC have a random chance of break. <br>
<br>
What I want is the ability to make a group that not require a Shaman or Chanters every single time. This expansion in many ways unbalanced classes alot more.<br>
<br>
It is a simple fact, you wont make a group in PoP if you not have a slower. I can easy keep up heal on a pet against mobs in PoV with just a chanter, with a cleric it is 10x harder. <br>
