<br>
How about a slow proc'ing pet weapon?   We give the thing to our pets and it will proc a certain % slow.  That would fit the magician line of spells a bit better..<br>
<br>
Better pet heals is definately something that we could get, IMO.   If nothing else, this would help us mitigate incoming damage.<br>
<br>
We're the only class that must recieve 100% of the mob's melee damage output.   We can't root the mob and back up.   We can't snare and outrun and we can't mezz.  These are all things we've accepted.   A better heal spell would allow us to stay alive longer and supplement the lack of anything but a pet.<br>
<br>
Personally, I don't like soloing.  Never have. Boring.  And I've always known that in the high-end game there is no soloing except for raw exp; which we can still do, but maybe not with the new PoP mobs.  I can kill robots in PoI solo, it eats up my mana but from watching a same level epic beast lord solo the same mobs, it eats up his mana too.<br>
<br>
Grouping is good from level 4 because you learn how to work with other players, not to mention you show them how valuable magicians can be.   If you solo through the game, you're kinda missing the point of a MMPORG, and certainly missing a great portion of the fun.<br>
<br>
With the introduction of the new Firebolt of Tallon (Crit for 3500 from a Magician?  Awesome!), the new pets that can hit top level mobs, cool pet summons, and all that great stuff - it's helped me find groups like never before.   When there's a Wizard LFG and me LFG, all things being equal I'm going to get the group.  And having LFG'd forever through the 30's, 40's and 50's, that's FINE BY ME.<br>
<br>
Plus.  The Epic pet CAN tank.  (probably the new pets can tank too.) With Aegolism I gauge his hit points at about 5500 - 6000.   That's pretty good.   I'm sure the AC ain't no 1400 like a good tank, but he really doesn't seem to have to be CH'd much more then you're average level 60 tank with &quot;decent&quot; gear.<br>
<br>
If you have a group with a chanter and a cleric, you're in for some EXCELLENT experience in PoI, PoD and PoV.  I've been in this type of group killing those level 60 spiders in PoN.   Best part is, cleric heals have NO aggro from mobs - so CH away and no dead cleric.  The epic pet keeps excellent aggro (when not in melee range..) so you can pretty much chain nuke from the start if it's a real tough mob.<br>
<br>
There's a lot that I would love to see on the Magician class, but for now I'm pretty happy with it.   I think it's overall one of the most fun classes to play. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cbreaker1212>CBreaker1212</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(11/12/02 3:08:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=413.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Ohh yea...</span><hr size=1> ... but fix the frigging GLARING bugs with:  DUELS, Frenzied Burnout, and the new PoP &quot;pet&quot; AA things. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=omegasyphon>omegasyphon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 607<br> <font color=#333333>(11/12/02 3:14:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=413.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  comment</span><hr size=1> im not sure we need a slow spell maybe one vs summoned mobs how ever it is a real problem in the game right now that most people wont even group with out a shaman or chanter because of their slow ability. their just isnt enough of them to go around <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUser